content.text: What is the stiffness matrix for this part of the groove structure?

I'm unable to directly view or interpret the image, but if the relevant part of the groove structure is indicated in an image and can be described as aligning along a specific direction based on predefined cases such as along the X-axis (left-to-right), Y-axis (bottom-to-top), diagonal in the YZ-plane, or entrance at the left-bottom, I can provide the corresponding stiffness matrix. You could describe the groove alignment, and I’ll give you the stiffness matrix based on that information.
